item.title: whew..
item.description: so I just finished this crazy project. it was really rough. but we got it done. barely. seriously. we barely made it. hehe. my cdr even broke so we had to magically find another CDr to burn the master with in 0.3seconds.. w00tin my spare time I have been hanging out with friends in #corporate. RULE. I enjoy it. you should come along. it is fun. hmm this weekend will be fun.
